      <title>韩国银行警告开发商利润缩水带来的债务风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/bank-of-korea-warns-of-developers-debt-risks-as-profits-shrink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行发布最新警告称，由于市场低迷对韩国开发商的盈利造成影响，它们的财务困境可能会进一步恶化，信贷风险持续给韩国经济蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/bank-of-korea-warns-of-developers-debt-risks-as-profits-shrink</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰将韩国股票评级上调至增持，因未来内存增长强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/hsbc-upgrades-korean-stocks-to-overweight-on-memory-growth-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司将韩国股票评级从中性上调至增持，理由是存储行业存在增长机会，且政府出台举措以提高估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/hsbc-upgrades-korean-stocks-to-overweight-on-memory-growth-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 01:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家为何上调中国经济增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-26/why-economists-are-raising-china-s-growth-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[接受彭博调查的经济学家目前表示，尽管消费支出放缓，但今年中国经济可能增长 5%，高于 5 月份预测的 4.9%。彭博电视台的 Minmin Low 报道。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-26/why-economists-are-raising-china-s-growth-forecasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 01:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
